          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-copy-1592843375130-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped shallot</strong> and <strong>cider vinegar</strong> with your <strong>sweet pepper relish</strong>, 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]<strong> </span>sugar </strong>and your<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Set aside to pickle – this is your<strong> quick-pickled cucumber relish</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
